11:21.000 --> 11:22.220
Whoa, no, no.

11:22.260 --> 11:24.480
She's frustrating and nutty
and, like...

11:24.530 --> 11:25.490
and annoying.

11:25.530 --> 11:27.960
She's very, very annoying.

11:28.010 --> 11:31.920
But she's a good mom,
and she's my friend,

11:31.970 --> 11:32.920
and, listen, like--

11:32.970 --> 11:35.270
I care about you so much,

11:35.320 --> 11:38.320
