16:40.190 --> 16:42.150
I would never want to shut out
anything about you.

16:42.190 --> 16:44.450
Because you're perfect.

16:44.500 --> 16:48.200
People say you don't find
the love of your life at 12,

16:48.240 --> 16:51.460
